data.comment: The match has started at Tele2 Arena.
Throw-in high up the field for Djurgarden in Stockholm.
In the minute 2, Can Djurgarden capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Sirius's half?
In Stockholm, Kalle Holmberg (Djurgarden) gets his head to the ball but the strike is cleared by an untiring defence.
Throw-in Djurgarden.
In the minute 3, Sirius awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Free kick Djurgarden.
Djurgarden have been awarded a corner by Andreas Ekberg.
In the minute 6, Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Sirius in their own half.
Free kick for Djurgarden in their own half.
Can Djurgarden capitalize from this dangerous free kick?
In the minute 10, At Tele2 Arena, Karl Larson has been yellow-carded for the away team.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Djurgarden push forward at Tele2 Arena and Fredrik Ulvestad gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Sirius defence.
In the minute 14, It's a goal kick for the away team in Stockholm.
Sirius awarded a free kick in their own half.
Andreas Ekberg awards Djurgarden a goal kick.
In the minute 16, Fredrik Ulvestad gets his shot on target but fails to score for Djurgarden.
Corner awarded to Djurgarden.
Free kick for Djurgarden in the half of Sirius.
In the minute 18, At Tele2 Arena, Djurgarden are penalized for being offside.
Ball goes out of play for a Sirius goal kick.
Can Sirius get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Djurgarden's half?
In the minute 20, In Stockholm Sirius's Axel Bjornstrom is caught offside.
Andreas Ekberg signals a Sirius throw-in in Djurgarden's half.
Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Sirius just outside Djurgarden's area.
In the minute 23, Goal kick for Djurgarden at Tele2 Arena.
Sirius awarded a free kick in their own half.
Throw-in for Sirius in the half of Djurgarden.
In the minute 25, Ball safe as Djurgarden is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In Stockholm a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Djurgarden are caught offside.
In the minute 27, Sirius make their first substitution with Johan Karlsson replacing Karl Larson.
The away team replace Jamie Roche with Daniel Jarl.
Free kick in a good position for Sirius!
In the minute 29, Sirius will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Djurgarden.
Axel Bjornstrom (Sirius) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
Sirius have a goal kick.
In the minute 32, Sirius to take a throw-in in Djurgarden territory.
Free kick for Djurgarden in their own half.
Stefano Vecchia for Sirius has been booked by Andreas Ekberg and receives a first yellow card.
In the minute 33, Play has been temporarily suspended for attention to Aslak Witry for Djurgarden who is writhing in pain on the pitch.
Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Sirius in their own half.
Fredrik Ulvestad (Djurgarden) has received a first yellow card.
In the minute 35, Aslak Witry for Djurgarden is back on the field again.
Throw-in for Sirius in their own half.
In Stockholm Djurgarden drive forward through Elliot Kack. His shot is on target but it's saved.
In the minute 37, Ball goes out of play for a Sirius goal kick.
Djurgarden are in shooting range from this free kick.
Djurgarden are coming forward and Jonathan Augustinsson gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
In the minute 39, It's a goal kick for the away team in Stockholm.
Throw-in for Djurgarden at Tele2 Arena.
Andreas Ekberg blows against Djurgarden's Kalle Holmberg for offside.
In the minute 41, Corner awarded to Sirius.
Djurgarden have a goal kick.
Djurgarden have been awarded a corner by Andreas Ekberg.
In the minute 44, Djurgarden have been awarded a corner by Andreas Ekberg.
Corner awarded to Djurgarden.
Djurgarden's Elliot Kack misses with an attempt on goal.
In the minute 45, Goal kick for Sirius at Tele2 Arena.
Andreas Ekberg awards Sirius a goal kick.
1 minutes of injury time will be added to the 1st half.
In the minute 45, Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Sirius.
The ref's whistle signals the end of the first-half.
The second half has started at Tele2 Arena.
In the minute 46, Can Djurgarden get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Sirius's half?
Andreas Ekberg awards the away team a throw-in.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
In the minute 48, Andreas Ekberg awards the away team a throw-in.
Sirius's Yukiya Sugita gets in a shot on goal at Tele2 Arena. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Throw-in for Sirius in the half of Djurgarden.
In the minute 50, Free kick for Sirius in the half of Djurgarden.
Djurgarden's Elliot Kack gets his shot away but it misses the target.
Andreas Ekberg awards Sirius a goal kick.
In the minute 52, Djurgarden to take a throw-in in Sirius territory.
Andreas Ekberg waits before resuming play because Haris Radetinac for Djurgarden is still down.
Throw-in for Djurgarden in their own half.
In the minute 55, Sirius have been awarded a corner by Andreas Ekberg.
Djurgarden awarded a free kick in their own half.
Haris Radetinac is back on his feet again.
In the minute 56, Ball goes out of play for a Sirius goal kick.
Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Sirius in their own half.
Djurgarden awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 57, Free kick Djurgarden.
Jesper Karlstrom (Djurgarden) gets a yellow card.
Stefano Vecchia (Sirius) has been booked for the second time by the referee and is off!
In the minute 62, Djurgarden are whistled for offside.
The away team have replaced Hjalmar Ekdal with Nahom Girmai. This is the third substitution made today by Henrik Rydstrom.
Kalle Holmberg is on target to give Djurgarden a 1-0 advantage.
In the minute 66, Thomas Lagerlof is making the team's first substitution at Tele2 Arena with Edward Chilufya replacing Nicklas Barkroth.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Stockholm.
Goal kick for Djurgarden at Tele2 Arena.
In the minute 69, Haris Radetinac (Djurgarden) gets in a header on goal but the attempt is cleared.
Corner awarded to Djurgarden.
Sirius have a goal kick.
In the minute 70, Andreas Ekberg signals a free kick to Sirius.
In Stockholm, Sirius push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
It's now 2-0 in Stockholm as Kalle Holmberg scores for Djurgarden.
In the minute 72, Great play from Edward Chilufya to set up the goal.
Throw-in Djurgarden.
Emir Kujovic is on a sub for Kalle Holmberg for Djurgarden.
In the minute 75, Free kick for Sirius in their own half.
Sirius are pushing forward but Adam Hellborg's finish is wide of the goal.
Djurgarden have a goal kick.
In the minute 77, Goal! Djurgarden extend their lead to 3-0 through Fredrik Ulvestad.
Curtis Edwards instrumental with a fine assist.
Laorent Shabani is replacing Adam Hellborg for Sirius at Tele2 Arena.
In the minute 78, Niklas Busch Thor is replacing Elias Andersson for the away team.
Sirius awarded a free kick in their own half.
Magnus Eriksson is on a sub for Curtis Edwards for Djurgarden.
In the minute 80, Djurgarden drive forward but Magnus Eriksson is judged offside.
Throw-in for Sirius at Tele2 Arena.
Ball safe as Djurgarden is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 81, Andreas Ekberg awards the home team a throw-in.
Edward Chilufya (Djurgarden) gets in a powerful header but the ball is cleared away.
Magnus Eriksson of Djurgarden gets in a strike, but is off target.
In the minute 83, Goal kick for Sirius at Tele2 Arena.
Djurgarden's Edward Chilufya gets in a shot but it is blocked by a Sirius defender.
Ball goes out of play for a Sirius goal kick.
In the minute 85, Fredrik Ulvestad for Djurgarden drives towards goal at Tele2 Arena. But the finish is unsuccessful.
In Stockholm Djurgarden attack through Fredrik Ulvestad. The finish is off target, however.
Andreas Ekberg awards Sirius a goal kick.
In the minute 86, Djurgarden take a comfortable 4-0 lead thanks to Fredrik Ulvestad.
That's a fine assist from Aslak Witry.
Andreas Ekberg signals a Djurgarden throw-in in Sirius's half.
In the minute 89, Magnus Eriksson of Djurgarden smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
Sirius awarded a throw-in in their own half.
3 minutes of injury time will be added to the 2nd half.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Djurgarden have been awarded a corner by Andreas Ekberg.
Djurgarden's Haris Radetinac is on target but unsuccessful.
Can Djurgarden get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Sirius's half?
Throw-in for Djurgarden in the half of Sirius.
The second-half is over. The match ends 4-0.
